{"2421310":{"success":true,"data":{"type":"game","name":"桃色武林","steam_appid":2421310,"required_age":0,"is_free":false,"detailed_description":"<h1>游戏提示<\/h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2421310\/extras\/20241205-151446.jpg?t=1733471180\" \/><\/p><\/p><br><h1>关于游戏<\/h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">《桃色武林》是一款新武侠题材的角色扮演游戏，在游戏中，玩家将扮演一个初出茅庐的江湖小生，在战斗和历练中结识红颜知己，并与她们共同闯荡这个充满危机与机遇的江湖世界。 <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">抛枕翠云光，绣衣闻异香。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">潜来珠锁动，惊觉银屏梦。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">脸慢笑盈盈，相看无限情。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">【游戏玩法】 <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">*多种战斗流派任你选择，上百种技能自由搭配组合，绝世武功助您驰骋江湖；<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">*战斗内随机产生道具、敌人以及升级奖励，每一局都是全新体验！<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">*地图中还有宝箱，开启宝箱可以获得技能<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">【主角简介】<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2421310\/extras\/萧.jpg?t=1733471180\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>飞鸿断霞，萧衡雁<\/strong><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">26岁，孤女，英气非凡，现任西子亭掌院。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2421310\/extras\/叶.jpg?t=1733471180\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>尹念念<\/strong><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">28岁，亲王妾，身材娇小，曾被男主父亲救过，对男主之父心生情愫，后将这份爱移情于男主。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2421310\/extras\/暮.jpg?t=1733471180\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>云行鹤影 暮寒雪<\/strong><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">24岁，雪山派。两年前受情人蛊惑，夺取秘籍，杀师并叛出师门，一直遭到门派追杀，后得男主相救，因中尸毒，委身男主，后欲提升修为，与男主“双修”，是男主上乘武学的启蒙老师。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2421310\/extras\/虞.jpg?t=1733471180\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>虞紫瑶<\/strong><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">20岁，鲁东堂，一年前因吴月先谋夺控制鲁东堂丈夫惨死，又被吴月先蹂躏玩弄。表面上是吴月先收服的女人，实际上却忍辱负重隐在吴月先身边伺机报仇，后因对吴月先动手复仇失败命悬一线，被男主以同类型双修功法所救。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2421310\/extras\/迦.jpg?t=1733471180\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>黑迦丽<\/strong><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">18岁，献王教教主，戴着恐怖面具统御众人，无人知其女儿身的秘密，后被男主撞破女子身份并发生亲密关系。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">【游戏特色】<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">超过10W字新武侠风格剧情<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">超过100张剧情CG<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">超过100条女角色中文配音<\/p>","about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">《桃色武林》是一款新武侠题材的角色扮演游戏，在游戏中，玩家将扮演一个初出茅庐的江湖小生，在战斗和历练中结识红颜知己，并与她们共同闯荡这个充满危机与机遇的江湖世界。 <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">抛枕翠云光，绣衣闻异香。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">潜来珠锁动，惊觉银屏梦。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">脸慢笑盈盈，相看无限情。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">【游戏玩法】 <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">*多种战斗流派任你选择，上百种技能自由搭配组合，绝世武功助您驰骋江湖；<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">*战斗内随机产生道具、敌人以及升级奖励，每一局都是全新体验！<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">*地图中还有宝箱，开启宝箱可以获得技能<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">【主角简介】<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2421310\/extras\/萧.jpg?t=1733471180\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>飞鸿断霞，萧衡雁<\/strong><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">26岁，孤女，英气非凡，现任西子亭掌院。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2421310\/extras\/叶.jpg?t=1733471180\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>尹念念<\/strong><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">28岁，亲王妾，身材娇小，曾被男主父亲救过，对男主之父心生情愫，后将这份爱移情于男主。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.a